High volume ceilings. Open floor plan design . Home automation package. Wood finish cabinets. Driveway w/ brick pavers. Solar panels. White fence in the backyard. Barbecue area new with all appliances to cook your favorite meals in the back patio. Covered terrace. Copper Creek is a beautiful, gated community w/ clubhouse, gym, party room, library, community pool, tennis, basketball, & playground area. Tenants occupied till July 15, 2024. Showings are with appointment only.
